{
  "stem": "14251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When we went into the attic, we tore up the stairs just ahead of the Gestapo, and the Levents pulled us in into the area that would get us to there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We came outside through a gate through which the postal wagons would drive on their routes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there, in front of the building-- and my father kept saying walk calmly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We are just out for a walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You couldn't look like someone who was getting away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He said, just walk calmly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I'm between my parents-- I still remember this-- we get out in front, and there were-- I don't remember, two, three trucks, kind of like army trucks you have to think, loaded with people standing.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now, the danger was that since we had lived there for some time, you shopped in your immediate neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So did maybe other people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was risky that someone might, hoping to get some personal advantage even out of this-- this happened also, you don't know what people do, or I'm caught, why are they walking-- could have shouted out, there they go, the Goldsteins, you know.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But this did not happen, and they walked calmly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So we really left with the clothes we had on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I mean, in the moments before they broke in we put on coats, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We had the good sense to do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nothing, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we walked calmly to the corner.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was another case of-- my job was not to step on the lines of these squares, you know, cement squares.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we picked up speed toward the end of that long, long block that was never going to end, past the kindergarten and all.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we caught the first streetcar that came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, this was downtown.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
